OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy on Wednesday with
OL,6,Ffurther outbreaks of mostly light
OL,7,Fdrizzle, mainly across the hills and
OL,8,Fmoors in the west. Some sunnier spells
OL,9,Ffirst thing in the east once low cloud
OL,10,Flifts. Light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudier this evening with a
OL,13,Fband of rain pushing across the
OL,14,Fregion. Turning drier overnight with
OL,15,Flengthy clear skies allowing for a
OL,16,Ftouch of frost in rural spots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
