OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA chilly but bright start
OL,6,Fwith sunnier spells in the east.
OL,7,FSunshine more hazy through the
OL,8,Fafternoon but otherwise staying fine
OL,9,Fand dry with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FTurning
OL,12,Funsettled over the Easter weekend with
OL,13,Fshowers or longer spells of rain.
OL,14,FGenerally drier and brighter through
OL,15,FSunday. Some strong and gusty winds
OL,16,Ftoo.
